ğŸ”„ Detailed Event Flows
1. Order Placement Flow
Portfolio BC â†’ [BuyOrderRequestedEvent] â†’ Market Engine
                                              â†“
                                    [CreateOrderCommand]
                                              â†“
                                         Order BC
